{"tid":437144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港珠澳橋連接路隧道爆龍噴水 !!!!!","createTime":"2017-10-15T17:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T11:27:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":98,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"845a378b538f2ebd77d0698d9eb1a703ba78e8f2","tid":437144,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"國家級基建項目港珠澳大橋香港段相關工程發生隧道「爆龍」噴水事故！連接大橋香港口岸及屯門第四十區的屯門至赤鱲角連接路，工程進度持續滯後，上月底趕工進行海底隧道工程期間，隧道內的連接管道牆壁更突然爆裂，大量地下水「噴泉式」激射入隧道內，工程人員慌忙搶修，結果噴水超過半分鐘後才成功「止血」。知情人士指今次事故懷疑涉及施工質量欠佳，導致管道無法承受地下水壓力而破裂，質疑路政署未有做好監管。有工程界人士更指一旦今次湧入工地的是源源不絕的海水，整條造價逾百億港元的隧道隨時報廢；關注團體擔心同類事故陸續有來，阻礙連接路的完工日期。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士透露，「爆龍」事故發於上月廿四日，連接香港口岸人工島的屯門至赤鱲角連接路－北面連接路項目，一條興建中的海底隧道內，其中一條行內稱為cross passage(小隧道)的連接管道出現裂縫，導致大量泥水湧入。從東網獲得的短片可見，泥水有如噴泉般橫向激射進隧道內，並不斷噴向附近的工程設備，地面亦慢慢出現積水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171016/photo/bkn-20171016000036507-1016_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171016004234\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171016%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171016000036507-1016_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171016004234&h=c2e456bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171016/bkn-20171016000036507-1016_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171016%2Fbkn-20171016000036507-1016_00822_001.html&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=cdac4bb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171016/bkn-20171016000036507-1016_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fe01bf727a17829ace678e1d7250106ef4360620","tid":437144,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:12:22.000Z","msg":"video<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS171015-14230-55-M&amp;d=1508083008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DONS171015-14230-55-M%26d%3D1508083008&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8623fc33\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS171015-14230-55-M&amp;d=1508083008</a>"},{"pid":"9778e0197889408d885c732ad21fc4a4ca254bcd","tid":437144,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13820cd494ee31c5a2c30ee886f939af43e5bdf","tid":437144,"uid":19454,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FXVTdB5x_qo/VO3as_nOmjI/AAAAAAAAEbA/30nRPi9QjCU/s400/20150223.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-FXVTdB5x_qo%2FVO3as_nOmjI%2FAAAAAAAAEbA%2F30nRPi9QjCU%2Fs400%2F20150223.gif&h=b2b40c69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d57ad2232be2d45c5a4782452b521eecd3b30a4","tid":437144,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a02773af842bc7eecf6cfd8fcac7b13b5735d78","tid":437144,"uid":57962,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f75e4f8073d8e445660170cdf739232d60efefc","tid":437144,"uid":71556,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d738554c648e7423f489ced75e21adde4d845494","tid":437144,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da98c089dcd09235b9d8b63b6a822634d149b75","tid":437144,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"f